	<title>Pressure-Cooker Sauerbraten Recipe: How to Make It</title>
	<meta name="description" content="One of my all-time favorite German dishes is sauerbraten, but I don&#39;t love that it normally takes five to 10 days to make. Using an electric pressure cooker, I think I&#39;ve captured that same distinctive flavor in less than two hours. —James Schend, Pleasant Prairie, Wisconsin"/>
