<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-24-24 pure-u-lg-24-24 pure-u-xl-24-24 dek-aff-wrapper">
	<div class="dek">
		<p>One of my all-time favorite German dishes is sauerbraten, but I don&#39;t love that it normally takes five to 10 days to make. Using an electric pressure cooker, I think I&#39;ve captured that same distinctive flavor in less than two hours. —James Schend, Pleasant Prairie, Wisconsin</p>	</div>
	</div>
